reviewText: Not a high quality documentory and also was not an Gaga sanctioned production. To qualify this, I am Mother's little monster (e.g. huge fan of Lady Gaga). I wasn't able to even finish watching it. Many of the spokespersons were irritating and obviously not true fans.
Captured with an excellent variety of interviewers--from 2009 through 2013--these recordings given extensive picture of this complex and many-sourced artist.
